title: WHISPERING SMITH -- Stake-Out ( pilot episode )
description:
Contrary to the IMDB, this is the pilot. How can I be sure ? Well, iIt's the only episode to end with " Produced in Association with the NBC Television Network ".

Another thing is the episodes listed towards the end of the series actually are among 6 that NBC never aired in 1961 All of them were among the early batch produced in 1959 and early 1960 with a different opening montage.  Most of the episodes were filmed throughout 1960. Audie Murphy went back to making movies after production ended
